%F A037581 From _Colin Barker_, Dec 27 2012: (Start)
%F A037581 a(n) = (3^(1+2*n) + 2*(-1)^n - 5)/20.
%F A037581 a(n) = 9*a(n-1) + a(n-2) - 9*a(n-3).
%F A037581 G.f.: x*(3*x+1) / ((x-1)*(x+1)*(9*x-1)). (End)
